addMPEventHandler 
Game: ArmA 2: Operation Arrowhead (1.55) 
Description: The format of handler is [type,command]. Check scripting topic Event 
 handlers for more information. The index of the current handler 
 is returned.  
Syntax:  
 unitName addMPEventHandler ["event", {action}]; 
Parameters: 
unitName: Object 
event: String 
action: Code 
Return Value: 
 Number or Nothing